<!doctype html>
<html lang="es-MX">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>PRO Enhanced Nutrition - Herramientas</title>

  <style>
    /* =========================
       PALETA C — PRO NEON
       ========================= */
    :root{
      --bg: #E6F1F6;
      --panel: #FFFFFF;
      --panel2: #F0F4FA;
      --stroke: #E2E8F0;

      --text: #1E293B;
      --muted: #64748B;

      --pink: #FF3FD5;
      --pink2:#FF6BE6;
      --cyan: #22C7E5;
      --shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);

      --r1: 26px;
      --r2: 18px;

      --orange: rgba(255, 140, 0, 1);
    }

    *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
    html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 600px at 15% 10%, rgba(255,63,213,0.18), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 600px at 85% 20%, rgba(255,107,230,0.14), transparent 58%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 140, 200, 0.20), rgba(255, 180, 220, 0.08)),
        var(--bg);
      min-height:100vh;
    }

    a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }

    .wrap{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding: 26px 18px 70px;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;

      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);

      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);

      border-radius: 999px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);

      position: sticky;
      top: 14px;
      z-index: 20;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .dot{
      width:12px;
      height:12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow:
        0 0 22px rgba(255,63,213,0.60),
        0 0 28px rgba(34,199,229,0.25);
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 900;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,63,213,0.18), rgba(34,199,229,0.16));
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0,0,0,0.40);
      cursor:pointer;
      transition: transform .12s ease, filter .12s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(1.06); }
    .btn:active{ transform: translateY(0px); filter: brightness(0.98); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero{
      margin-top: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.10), rgba(255,255,255,0.06));
      border-radius: var(--r1);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero:before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:-120px -160px auto auto;
      width: 360px;
      height: 360px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(34,199,229,0.22), transparent 60%);
      filter: blur(8px);
      transform: rotate(18deg);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .hero:after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto auto -160px -160px;
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,63,213,0.22), transparent 60%);
      filter: blur(10px);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .heroInner{
      position:relative;
      padding: 26px;
    }

    .kicker{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.45px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    }
    .kicker .spark{
      width:10px;
      height:10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,199,229,0.35);
      transform: rotate(15deg);
    }

    h1{
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4.3vw, 50px);
      line-height: 1.03;
      letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    }

    .heroSubtitle{
      margin: 4px 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(20px, 2.6vw, 30px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .sub{
      margin:0;
      max-width: 70ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .toolBox2{
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:18px 22px 18px 26px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:var(--panel);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:16px;
      color:var(--text);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display:block;
      max-width:700px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
      position:relative;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      overflow:hidden;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .toolSub{
      display:block;
      margin-top:6px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }

    .infoBox{
      margin-top:16px;
      padding:22px 22px 22px 26px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:var(--panel);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      max-width:900px;
      margin-left:0;
      margin-right:auto;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .infoBox::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      top:0;
      bottom:0;
      width:8px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34,199,229,0.45), rgba(34,199,229,0.20));
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-radius:18px 0 0 18px;
    }

    .infoTitle{
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .infoBox p{
      font-size:15px;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.6;
      margin:0 0 10px;
    }

    /* =========================
       CENTER BOX
       ========================= */
    .centerBox{
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:18px 26px;
      border-radius:22px;
      background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.30);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);

      color: #1E293B;
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:900;
      text-align:center;
      letter-spacing:0.6px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      line-height:1.35;

      box-shadow:
        0 20px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 40px rgba(255,140,0,0.28);

      max-width:780px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;

      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .centerBox::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      left:-20%;
      top:-60%;
      width:60%;
      height:220%;
      transform: rotate(20deg);
      animation: glassMove 6s linear infinite;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      filter: blur(2px);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .centerBox::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      top:0;
      bottom:0;
      width:10px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 170, 60, 0.9), rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.5));
      border-radius:22px 0 0 22px;
      opacity:0.75;
    }

    @keyframes glassMove {
      0%   { transform: translateX(-120%) rotate(20deg); }
      100% { transform: translateX(220%) rotate(20deg); }
    }

    /* =========================
       FENOTIPOS
       ========================= */
    .fenotipoGrid{
      margin-top: 16px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .fenotipoCard{
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 18px 18px 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;

      border: 1px solid rgba(140, 90, 255, 0.22);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(140, 90, 255, 0.14), rgba(140, 90, 255, 0.06));

      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);

      box-shadow:
        0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.12),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.22) inset;

      transition: transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease;
    }

    .fenotipoCard::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      left:-30%;
      top:-80%;
      width:60%;
      height:260%;
      transform: rotate(18deg);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      filter: blur(10px);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .fenotipoCard h3{
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .fenotipoCard h3 span{
      display: block;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .fenotipoCard ul{
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .fenotipoCard li{ margin: 6px 0; }

    .fenotipoCard:hover{
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow:
        0 28px 75px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.28) inset,
        0 0 34px rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .fenotipoCard.cardActiva{
      animation: pulseCard 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
      outline: 2px solid rgba(255,120,0,0.65);
      box-shadow:
        0 34px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.22),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.30) inset,
        0 0 55px rgba(255,120,0,0.35);
    }

    @keyframes pulseCard{
      0%{ transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.00); }
      50%{ transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02); }
      100%{ transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.00); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .fenotipoGrid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* =========================
       SELECTOR CRITERIOS SOP
       ========================= */
    .criteriaWrap{
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .criteriaBox{
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .criteriaRow{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .criteriaRow:last-child{ border-bottom: 0; }

    .critText{
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .toggleBtn{
      min-width: 70px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, background .15s ease, border-color .15s ease;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .toggleBtn[data-val="no"]{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      color: #2d3a45;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .toggleBtn[data-val="si"]{
      background: rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.20);
      border-color: rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.65);
      color: #1c2b35;
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 0 2px rgba(255,120,0,0.28),
        0 0 35px rgba(255,120,0,0.35);
    }

    .toggleBtn:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .resultBox{
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 18px 18px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      transition: background .2s ease, border-color .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
    }

    .resultBox.isResult{ animation: pulseResult 1.25s ease-in-out infinite; }

    @keyframes pulseResult{
      0%   { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
      50%  { transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.01); }
      100% { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
    }

    .resTitle{
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(30,40,50,0.85);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .resMain{
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1e2f3a;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .resFenotipo{
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1e2f3a;
    }

    .resMeta{
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(30,40,50,0.75);
    }

    .resultBox.resA{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.55);
      background: rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0 0 40px rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.25);
    }
    .resultBox.resB{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.60);
      background: rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0 0 45px rgba(255, 120, 0, 0.25);
    }
    .resultBox.resC{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 200, 0, 0.60);
      background: rgba(255, 200, 0, 0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0 0 45px rgba(255, 200, 0, 0.22);
    }
    .resultBox.resD{
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 220, 140, 0.60);
      background: rgba(0, 220, 140, 0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0 0 45px rgba(0, 220, 140, 0.22);
    }
    .resultBox.resNeutral{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,120,0,0.35);
      background: rgba(255,120,0,0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.14), 0 0 40px rgba(255,120,0,0.18);
    }

    /* =========================
       BOTÓN REINICIAR
       ========================= */
    .resetWrap{
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .resetBtn{
      padding: 12px 26px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .6px;

      border: 1px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.55);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      color: #1E293B;

      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;

      box-shadow:
        0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.10),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 22px rgba(255,63,213,0.22);

      transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, filter .18s ease;
    }

    .resetBtn:hover{
      filter: brightness(1.03);
      animation: pulseReset 1.15s ease-in-out infinite;
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.40) inset,
        0 0 36px rgba(255,63,213,0.38),
        0 0 60px rgba(255,107,230,0.22);
    }

    .resetBtn:active{
      transform: translateY(1px) scale(0.99);
      filter: brightness(0.98);
    }

    .exportBtn{
      padding: 12px 26px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .6px;

      border: 1px solid rgba(34,199,229,0.55);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(34,199,229,0.20), rgba(255,63,213,0.18));
      color: #0f172a;

      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;

      box-shadow:
        0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.10),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 22px rgba(34,199,229,0.22);

      transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, filter .18s ease;
    }

    .exportBtn:hover{
      filter: brightness(1.03);
      animation: pulseReset 1.15s ease-in-out infinite;
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.40) inset,
        0 0 36px rgba(34,199,229,0.30),
        0 0 60px rgba(255,63,213,0.18);
    }

    .exportBtn:active{
      transform: translateY(1px) scale(0.99);
      filter: brightness(0.98);
    }

    @keyframes pulseReset{
      0%   { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
      50%  { transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02); }
      100% { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
    }

    /* =========================
       RECUADRO 2-COLUMNAS (SI/NO amarillo)
       ========================= */
    .haBox{
      margin-top: 1cm;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .haRow{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 210px;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
    }
    .haRow:last-child{ border-bottom: 0; }

    .haText{
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: #1f2c36;
    }

    .haYN{
      justify-self: end;
      width: 200px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .7px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, background .15s ease, border-color .15s ease;
      user-select: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .haYN[data-val="no"]{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.75);
      color: #111827;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .haYN[data-val="si"]{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.95);
      border-color: rgba(255, 200, 0, 0.85);
      color: #0b1220;
      box-shadow:
        0 16px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 26px rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.35);
    }
    .haYN:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* =========================
       CALCULADORA % GRASA + TABLA DERECHA
       ========================= */
    .bfSection{
      margin-top: 3cm;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
    }

    .bfTitle{
      text-align:center;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .3px;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .bfLayout{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .bfCard{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      padding: 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .bfHint{
      margin: 2px 0 12px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align:center;
      line-height:1.35;
    }

    .bfGrid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .bfField{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap: 7px;
    }

    .bfLabel{
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #334155;
      letter-spacing: .4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .bfInput, .bfSelect{
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
      outline: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .bfInput:focus, .bfSelect:focus{
      border-color: rgba(255,63,213,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,63,213,0.10);
    }

    .bfActions{
      margin-top: 12px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .bfBtn{
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      cursor:pointer;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,63,213,0.20), rgba(34,199,229,0.18));
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      transition: transform .12s ease, filter .12s ease;
    }
    .bfBtn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(1.03); }
    .bfBtn:active{ transform: translateY(0px); filter: brightness(0.98); }

    .bfBtn.secondary{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }

    .bfResult{
      margin-top: 12px;
      text-align:center;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,63,213,0.06);
    }
    .bfPct{
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#0f172a;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .bfSubRes{
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height:1.35;
    }

    .bfTableCard{
      position: relative;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .bfTableTitle{
      text-align:center;
      font-weight: 1000;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing:.35px;
      color:#111827;
      margin: 4px 0 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .bfTableWrap{
      position: relative;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    }

    .bfTable{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .bfTable th, .bfTable td{
      padding: 10px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      text-align: left;
      color:#0f172a;
      font-weight: 800;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .bfTable th{
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#334155;
    }

    .bfTable tr:last-child td{ border-bottom: 0; }

    .bfRowLabel{
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#111827;
    }

    .bfSectionDivider{
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      color: #334155;
      font-weight: 1000;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .bfRowActive{
      background: rgba(255,63,213,0.06);
      outline: 2px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.28);
      outline-offset: -2px;
    }

    .bfCellActive{
      background: rgba(255,63,213,0.14) !important;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 2px rgba(255,63,213,0.22) inset,
        0 0 18px rgba(255,63,213,0.18);
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 1000;
    }

    .bfArrow{
      position:absolute;
      left: -12px;
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      border-top: 9px solid transparent;
      border-bottom: 9px solid transparent;
      border-right: 14px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.95);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.20));
      opacity: 0;
      transition: top .18s ease, opacity .18s ease;
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .bfArrowLabel{
      position:absolute;
      left: -128px;
      width: 112px;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.35);
      font-weight: 1000;
      font-size: 12px;
      color:#111827;
      text-align:center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: top .18s ease, opacity .18s ease;
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .bfNote{
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-align:center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* =========================
       EVALUADOR SALUD METABÓLICA (MetS)
       ========================= */
    .msSection{
      margin-top: 3cm;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
    }

    .msHeader{
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #111827;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.38);
      background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 45px rgba(255,140,0,0.28);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .msHeader::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:-40% -30% auto auto;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.35), transparent 60%);
      filter: blur(10px);
      transform: rotate(18deg);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .msCard{
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .msTable{
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .msTable td{
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      vertical-align: middle;
      font-weight: 900;
      color:#0f172a;
    }
    .msTable tr:last-child td{ border-bottom: 0; }

    .msLeftGreen{
      background: rgba(120, 220, 120, 0.35);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .msRightYellow{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.55);
      width: 210px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .msYN{
      width: 180px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .7px;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, background .15s ease, border-color .15s ease;
    }
    .msYN[data-val="no"]{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.75);
      color:#111827;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .msYN[data-val="si"]{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.95);
      border-color: rgba(255, 200, 0, 0.85);
      color:#0b1220;
      box-shadow:
        0 16px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 26px rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.35);
    }
    .msYN:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .msInterpretRow td{
      background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.25) !important;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      font-weight: 1000;
    }

    .msInterpretText{
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#111827;
    }

    /* =========================
       ICC
       ========================= */
    .iccSection{
      margin-top: 3cm;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
    }

    .iccLayout{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      transform: translate(-22px, -38px);
    }

    .iccCard{
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .iccTitle{
      background: rgba(255, 215, 90, 0.85);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#111827;
    }

    .iccValueWrap{
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#0f172a;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    .iccValue{
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      min-width: 90px;
    }

    .iccValue.isHigh{
      background: rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.10);
      border-color: rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.45);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 40px rgba(255, 60, 80, 0.22);
      animation: iccPulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes iccPulse{
      0%{ transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
      50%{ transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02); }
      100%{ transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.00); }
    }

    .iccRowPink{
      background: rgba(255, 160, 190, 0.45);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#111827;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .iccRowBlue{
      background: rgba(140, 190, 255, 0.45);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#111827;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .iccImageCard{
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .iccImageCard img{
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display:block;
      border-radius: 14px;
    }

    /* =========================
       NOTAS (ACORDEÓN)
       ========================= */
    .notesSection{
      margin-top: 1cm;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
    }

    .notesCard{
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.80);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .accItem{ border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    .accItem:last-child{ border-bottom: 0; }

    details.acc{ padding: 0; }

    summary.accSum{
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;

      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,63,213,0.10), rgba(34,199,229,0.10));
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#0f172a;
    }

    summary.accSum::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }

    .accLeft{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .accPill{
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,199,229,0.25);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .accTitle{
      font-size: 13px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .accChevron{
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      transition: transform .22s ease, filter .22s ease;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    details[open] .accChevron{
      transform: rotate(180deg);
      filter: brightness(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }

    .accBody{
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
      color: var(--text);
      animation: accFade .22s ease;
    }

    @keyframes accFade{
      from{ opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-2px); }
      to{ opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); }
    }

    .notesMeta{
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#0f172a;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }

    .notesText{
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .notesText strong{ color:#0f172a; }

    .notesList{
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .notesList li{ margin: 6px 0; }

    .notesSubHead{
      margin: 14px 0 6px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color:#0f172a;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }

    .notesDivider{
      margin: 14px 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      border: 0;
    }

    /* =========================
       PAUTAS ADICIONALES
       ========================= */
    .pautasSection{
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
    }

    .pautasCard{
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.34);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.14),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 44px rgba(255,140,0,0.18);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .pautasHeader{
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#0f172a;
      background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.14);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
    }

    .pautasHeader:before{
      content:"";
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,140,0,0.22);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .pautasBody{
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
    }

    .pautasText{
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .pautasList{
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .pautasList li{ margin: 6px 0; }

    /* =========================
       ABORDAJE IDEAL
       ========================= */
    .abSection{
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left:auto;
      margin-right:auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .abTopGrid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .abCard{
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,199,229,0.28);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.12),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .abHeader{
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#0f172a;
      background: rgba(34,199,229,0.10);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .abHeader .tag{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,63,213,0.28);
      background: rgba(255,63,213,0.10);
      font-weight: 1000;
      font-size: 12px;
      color:#0f172a;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .abHeader .tagDot{
      width:8px; height:8px; border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(34,199,229,0.22);
    }

    .abBody{
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
    }

    .abText{
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .abList{
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .abList li{ margin: 6px 0; }

    .abGrid4{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .abMiniHeader{
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .25px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color:#0f172a;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,63,213,0.10), rgba(34,199,229,0.10));
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
    }

    .abMiniHeader:before{
      content:"";
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,199,229,0.20);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .abCard.isActive{
      outline: 2px solid rgba(255,120,0,0.55);
      box-shadow:
        0 26px 70px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 44px rgba(255,120,0,0.22);
    }

    .abNote{
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.32);
      background: rgba(255,140,0,0.10);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      color:#0f172a;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .abTopGrid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .abGrid4{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* =========================
       DIAGNÓSTICOS DIFERENCIALES (nueva sección)
       ========================= */
    .ddSection{
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .ddCard{
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 70, 239, 0.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.12),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset,
        0 0 44px rgba(217,70,239,0.10);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ddHeader{
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: .35px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #0f172a;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(217,70,239,0.10), rgba(59,130,246,0.10));
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .ddHeader::before{
      content: "";
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pink), var(--cyan));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,199,229,0.22);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .ddBody{
      padding: 18px 18px 22px;
    }

    .ddIntro{
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .ddIntro strong{
      color: #334155;
    }

    .ddGrid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .ddMimicCard{
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 16px 16px 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(140, 90, 255, 0.18);
      border-left: 5px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.75);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow:
        0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.07),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.22) inset;
      transition: transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease;
    }

    .ddMimicCard:hover{
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow:
        0 22px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.13),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.28) inset,
        0 0 30px rgba(255,120,0,0.18);
    }

    .ddMimicTitle{
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 14.5px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #0f172a;
      letter-spacing: .15px;
    }

    .ddMimicText{
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 13.5px;
    }

    .ddMimicList{
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .ddMimicList li{ margin: 5px 0; }

    .ddAlertBox{
      margin-top: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,60,80,0.08), rgba(255,140,0,0.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,60,80,0.20);
      box-shadow:
        0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),
        0 0 30px rgba(255,60,80,0.12);
    }

    .ddAlertTitle{
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      color: #991b1b;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .ddAlertTitle::before{
      content: "";
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #ef4444, #f97316);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .ddAlertList{
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: #7c2d12;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 13.5px;
    }
    .ddAlertList li{ margin: 5px 0; }

    .ddFooterNote{
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .ddFooterNote strong{
      color: #334155;
      font-style: normal;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .ddGrid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* =========================
       BOTONES FLOTANTES (WA + IG)
       ========================= */
    .floatBtns{
      position: fixed;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: 18px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      z-index: 999;
    }

    .floatBtn{
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset;
      transition: transform .14s ease, filter .14s ease;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .floatBtn:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); filter: brightness(1.05); }
    .floatBtn:active{ transform: translateY(0px) scale(0.98); }

    .floatBtn.wa{
      outline: 2px solid rgba(34, 199, 229, 0.22);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 32px rgba(34,199,229,0.22),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset;
    }
    .floatBtn.ig{
      outline: 2px solid rgba(255, 63, 213, 0.22);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        0 0 34px rgba(255,63,213,0.20),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.35) inset;
    }

    .floatBtn svg{
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    a.floatBtn{
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px){
      .bfLayout{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bfArrowLabel{ left: -118px; }
      .iccLayout{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; transform: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .criteriaRow{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .toggleBtn{ width: 100%; }
      .resetBtn{ width: 100%; }

      .haRow{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .haYN{ width: 100%; justify-self: stretch; }

      .bfGrid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bfActions{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bfArrowLabel{ display:none; }

      .msRightYellow{ width: auto; }
      .msYN{ width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrap">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span>PRO Enhanced Nutrition</span>
      </div>

      <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/528132216529?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20ponerme%20en%20contacto%20con%20PRO%20Enhanced%20Nutrition." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Contactar</a>
    </header>

    <main class="hero" id="inicio">
      <div class="heroInner">
        <div class="kicker"><span class="spark" aria-hidden="true"></span> Estructura • Métricas • Resultados</div>

        <h1>Identificador de Fenotipo</h1>

        <h2 class="heroSubtitle">de Síndrome de Ovario Poliquístico y Salud Metabólica</h2>

        <p class="sub">
          Herramienta diseñada para identificar el fenotipo de SOP, evaluar salud metabólica
          y orientar decisiones clínicas y nutricionales de forma estructurada.
        </p>

        <div class="toolBox2" role="note" aria-label="Herramienta">
          <strong>Herramienta Identificador de Fenotipo de SOP</strong>
          <span class="toolSub">Evaluación clínica y metabólica estructurada</span>
        </div>

        <div class="infoBox">
          <div class="infoTitle">¿Qué es el Síndrome de Ovario Poliquístico?</div>
          <p>El Síndrome de Ovario Poliquístico (SOP) es un trastorno endocrino–metabólico crónico y complejo que afecta principalmente a mujeres en edad reproductiva.</p>
          <p>En México, su prevalencia varía: estimaciones conservadoras lo sitúan en 6 %, pero estudios recientes elevan la cifra a 21–22 %.</p>
          <p>De acuerdo con los criterios de Rotterdam (2003), se requieren 2 de 3 criterios para el diagnóstico de SOP y asignación de fenotipo.</p>
          <p>A nivel global, afecta entre 6 % y 13 %.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="centerBox">
          FENOTIPOS, UNA FORMA DE CLASIFICAR A LAS PACIENTES
        </div>

        <div class="fenotipoGrid" id="fenotipos">
          <div class="fenotipoCard" data-feno="A">
            <h3>Fenotipo A <span>(Alteraciones menstruales y/o amenorrea + Hiperandrogenismo + Ovarios poliquísticos)</span></h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Es el más severo: cumple los 3 criterios.</li>
              <li>Mayor riesgo de resistencia a la insulina, síndrome metabólico y obesidad central.</li>
              <li>Elevada prevalencia de dislipidemias (↑ triglicéridos, ↓ HDL).</li>
              <li>Mayor riesgo de infertilidad y ciclos anovulatorios persistentes.</li>
              <li>Alta carga de síntomas visibles: acné, hirsutismo, alopecia androgénica.</li>
              <li>Mayor inflamación sistémica y riesgo cardiovascular.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="fenotipoCard" data-feno="B">
            <h3>Fenotipo B <span>(Alteraciones menstruales y/o amenorrea + Hiperandrogenismo)</span></h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Similar al fenotipo A pero sin morfología poliquística en ultrasonido.</li>
              <li>Elevado riesgo metabólico y resistencia a la insulina.</li>
              <li>Síntomas severos de hiperandrogenismo.</li>
              <li>Riesgo aumentado de infertilidad.</li>
              <li>Perfil lipídico con mayor probabilidad de alteración.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="fenotipoCard" data-feno="C">
            <h3>Fenotipo C <span>(Hiperandrogenismo + Ovarios poliquísticos)</span></h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Fenotipo ovulatorio (ciclos regulares).</li>
              <li>Riesgo metabólico intermedio.</li>
              <li>Síntomas de hiperandrogenismo presentes.</li>
              <li>Riesgo moderado de alteraciones glucémicas.</li>
              <li>Mejor pronóstico reproductivo que A y B.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="fenotipoCard" data-feno="D">
            <h3>Fenotipo D <span>(Alteraciones menstruales y/o amenorrea + Ovarios poliquísticos)</span></h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Fenotipo más leve, sin hiperandrogenismo.</li>
              <li>Menor riesgo metabólico.</li>
              <li>Puede presentar infertilidad por alteraciones menstruales.</li>
              <li>Baja carga de síntomas visibles.</li>
              <li>Buena respuesta a intervención dietética y ejercicio.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="criteriaWrap">
          <div class="criteriaBox" aria-label="Criterios SOP Rotterdam 2003">
            <div class="criteriaRow">
              <div class="critText">Alteraciones menstruales y/o amenorrea</div>
              <button class="toggleBtn" type="button" data-key="mens" data-val="no">NO</button>
            </div>

            <div class="criteriaRow">
              <div class="critText">
                Morfología de ovario poliquístico (MOP): ≥20 folículos antrales de 2–9 mm en al menos un ovario
                (o ≥12 folículos según criterio clásico) y/o volumen ovárico ≥10 mL en al menos un ovario.
              </div>
              <button class="toggleBtn" type="button" data-key="mop" data-val="no">NO</button>
            </div>

            <div class="criteriaRow">
              <div class="critText">Hiperandrogenismo (clínico o bioquímico)</div>
              <button class="toggleBtn" type="button" data-key="ha" data-val="no">NO</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="resultBox resNeutral" id="fenotipoResultado" aria-live="polite">
            <div class="resTitle">Resultado</div>
            <div class="resMain" id="resMain">Selecciona al menos 2 criterios para SOP (Rotterdam 2003).</div>
            <div class="resFenotipo" id="resFenotipo">—</div>
            <div class="resMeta" id="resMeta">Criterios positivos: 0/3</div>
          </div>

          <div class="resetWrap" style="gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <button class="resetBtn" id="btnReset" type="button">Reiniciar evaluación</button>
            <button class="exportBtn" id="btnExportWord" type="button">Exportar resultados a Word</button>
          </div>

          <div class="haBox" id="haExtraBox">
            <div class="haRow">
              <div class="haText">
                <strong>Hiperandrogenismo bioquímico:</strong> Posibles valores elevados de andrógenos como testosterona,
                androstenediona, dehidroepiandrosterona (DHEA) y dehidroepiandrosterona sulfato (DHEA-S).
              </div>
              <button class="haYN" type="button" id="haBioBtn" data-val="no">NO</button>
            </div>

            <div class="haRow">
              <div class="haText">
                <strong>Hiperandrogenismo clínico:</strong> Síndrome SAHA (Seborrea, Alopecia de patrón androgénico, Hirsutismo),
                acné.
              </div>
              <button class="haYN" type="button" id="haClinBtn" data-val="no">NO</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="bfSection" id="bfSection">
            <h3 class="bfTitle">Calculadora de porcentaje de grasa aproximado</h3>

            <div class="bfLayout">
              <div class="bfCard">
                <div class="bfHint">
                  Basado en fórmula US Navy (aproximación). Ingresa medidas en <strong>cm</strong> (se convierten a pulgadas internamente).
                  <br>El <strong>peso (kg)</strong> se usa para estimar <strong>kg de grasa</strong> y <strong>masa magra</strong>.
                </div>

                <div class="bfGrid">
                  <div class="bfField">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Sexo</div>
                    <select class="bfSelect" id="bfSex">
                      <option value="female">Mujer</option>
                      <option value="male">Hombre</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>

                  <div class="bfField">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Altura (cm)</div>
                    <input class="bfInput" id="bfHeight" type="number" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="Ej. 170" />
                  </div>

                  <div class="bfField">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Peso (kg)</div>
                    <input class="bfInput" id="bfWeight" type="number" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="Ej. 75" />
                  </div>

                  <div class="bfField">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Cuello (cm)</div>
                    <input class="bfInput" id="bfNeck" type="number" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="Ej. 35" />
                  </div>

                  <div class="bfField">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Cintura / Abdomen (cm)</div>
                    <input class="bfInput" id="bfWaist" type="number" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="Ej. 80" />
                  </div>

                  <div class="bfField" id="bfHipWrap">
                    <div class="bfLabel">Cadera (cm) (para mujer en %grasa • necesaria para ICC)</div>
                    <input class="bfInput" id="bfHip" type="number" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="Ej. 100" />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bfActions">
                  <button class="bfBtn" id="bfCalc" type="button">Calcular % grasa</button>
                  <button class="bfBtn secondary" id="bfClear" type="button">Limpiar</button>
                </div>

                <div class="bfResult" id="bfResultBox">
                  <p class="bfPct" id="bfPct">—</p>
                  <p class="bfSubRes" id="bfDetail">Completa los campos y presiona <strong>Calcular</strong>.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bfNote">
                  Para hombre se usa abdomen/cintura; para mujer se usa cintura + cadera. (ICC usa cintura/cadera).
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bfCard bfTableCard">
                <div class="bfTableTitle">Clasificación según porcentaje</div>

                <div class="bfTableWrap" id="bfTableWrap">
                  <div class="bfArrow" id="bfArrow"></div>
                  <div class="bfArrowLabel" id="bfArrowLabel"></div>

                  <table class="bfTable" id="bfTable">
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>Clasificación</th>
                        <th>Hombres</th>
                        <th>Mujeres</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <tr id="row-delgado">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Delgado</td>
                        <td>&lt; 8%</td>
                        <td>&lt; 15%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-optimo">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Óptimo</td>
                        <td>8–15%</td>
                        <td>15–20%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-sobrepeso">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Sobrepeso</td>
                        <td>15–20%</td>
                        <td>20–25%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-preobeso">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Pre-obeso</td>
                        <td>20–25%</td>
                        <td>25–32%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-obeso">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Obeso</td>
                        <td>&ge; 25%</td>
                        <td>&ge; 32%</td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr class="bfSectionDivider">
                        <td colspan="3">Atletas</td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr id="row-atleta-corre">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Corredores larga distancia</td>
                        <td>4–9%</td>
                        <td>6–15%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-lucha">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Luchadores</td>
                        <td>4–10%</td>
                        <td>—</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-gim">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Gimnastas</td>
                        <td>4–10%</td>
                        <td>10–17%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-cult">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Culturistas (élite)</td>
                        <td>5–8%</td>
                        <td>10–15%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-nada">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Nadadores</td>
                        <td>5–11%</td>
                        <td>14–24%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-basket">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Jugadores basket</td>
                        <td>7–11%</td>
                        <td>18–27%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-remo">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Remo</td>
                        <td>11–15%</td>
                        <td>18–24%</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr id="row-atleta-tenis">
                        <td class="bfRowLabel">Tenistas</td>
                        <td>14–17%</td>
                        <td>19–22%</td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>

                <div class="bfNote" id="bfClassNote">La flecha se posiciona cuando calculas un resultado.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="msSection" id="msSection">
            <div class="msHeader">Evaluador de salud metabólica</div>

            <div class="msCard">
              <table class="msTable" aria-label="Criterios Síndrome Metabólico">
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen">Cintura elevada (Hombres ≥102 cm / Mujeres ≥88 cm)</td>
                    <td class="msRightYellow">
                      <button class="msYN" type="button" data-key="waist" data-val="no">NO</button>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen">Triglicéridos ≥150 mg/dL</td>
                    <td class="msRightYellow">
                      <button class="msYN" type="button" data-key="tg" data-val="no">NO</button>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen">HDL bajo (H &lt;40 / M &lt;50 mg/dL)</td>
                    <td class="msRightYellow">
                      <button class="msYN" type="button" data-key="hdl" data-val="no">NO</button>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen">Presión arterial ≥130/85 mmHg</td>
                    <td class="msRightYellow">
                      <button class="msYN" type="button" data-key="bp" data-val="no">NO</button>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen">Glucosa en ayunas ≥100 mg/dL</td>
                    <td class="msRightYellow">
                      <button class="msYN" type="button" data-key="glu" data-val="no">NO</button>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr class="msInterpretRow">
                    <td colspan="2" class="msInterpretText" id="msInterpret">Interpretación de criterios</td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td class="msLeftGreen" id="msBottomText" colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">
                      No cumple los criterios para síndrome metabólico, evaluar más.
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="iccSection" id="iccSection">
            <div class="iccLayout">
              <div class="iccCard">
                <div class="iccTitle">Índice cintura-cadera (ICC)</div>

                <div class="iccValueWrap">
                  <span class="iccValue" id="iccValue">#DIV/0!</span>
                </div>

                <div class="iccRowPink">
                  ICC PARA MUJERES (&gt; 0.85) &nbsp;&nbsp; Revisar nota adjunta
                </div>
                <div class="iccRowBlue">
                  ICC PARA HOMBRES (&gt; 0.95) &nbsp;&nbsp; Revisar nota adjunta
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="iccImageCard">
                <img src="obesidad_tipos.png" alt="Tipos de obesidad: androide vs ginecoide" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="notesSection" id="notesSection">
            <div class="notesCard">
              <div class="accItem">
                <details class="acc" open>
                  <summary class="accSum">
                    <span class="accLeft">
                      <span class="accPill" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                      <span class="accTitle">Notas Adjuntas</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="accChevron" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none">
                        <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </summary>

                  <div class="accBody">
                    <p class="notesMeta">Raúl Vargas</p>

                    <p class="notesText">
                      El <strong>Índice de Cintura-Cadera (ICC)</strong> es diferente para mujeres y hombres:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="notesList">
                      <li><strong>En mujeres</strong>, el punto de corte promedio es <strong>&gt; 0.85</strong>. A mayor cifra, mayor probabilidad de riesgo cardiometabólico (según el contexto clínico).</li>
                      <li><strong>En hombres</strong>, el punto de corte promedio es <strong>&gt; 0.95</strong>.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <hr class="notesDivider" />

                    <p class="notesText">Según la distribución de grasa, se puede clasificar en:</p>

                    <p class="notesSubHead">Obesidad androide (más común en hombres), forma "manzana"</p>
                    <p class="notesText">Puede asociarse a:</p>
                    <ul class="notesList">
                      <li>Resistencia a la insulina</li>
                      <li>Intolerancia a la glucosa</li>
                      <li>Diabetes mellitus tipo 2</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="notesText">Zonas frecuentes: abdomen, espalda baja, cintura.</p>

                    <p class="notesSubHead">Obesidad ginecoide (más común en mujeres), forma "pera"</p>
                    <p class="notesText">Puede asociarse a:</p>
                    <ul class="notesList">
                      <li>Enfermedades de la vesícula</li>
                      <li>Várices</li>
                      <li>Constipación</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="notesText">Zonas frecuentes: cadera, muslos, piernas.</p>

                    <hr class="notesDivider" />

                    <p class="notesSubHead">RECOMENDACIÓN</p>
                    <p class="notesText">En cuanto a estudios de laboratorio, se aconseja solicitar:</p>
                    <ul class="notesList">
                      <li>Glucosa en ayunas</li>
                      <li>Insulina en ayunas</li>
                      <li><strong>HbA1c (hemoglobina glicosilada)</strong></li>
                      <li>Perfil lipídico completo</li>
                      <li>Índice aterogénico</li>
                      <li>PCR ultrasensible</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="notesText">
                      Correlacionar con composición corporal, circunferencias y clínica. Un objetivo razonable: pérdida de grasa de 5–10% a mediano plazo.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="accItem">
                <details class="acc">
                  <summary class="accSum">
                    <span class="accLeft">
                      <span class="accPill" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                      <span class="accTitle">Vista rápida</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="accChevron" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none">
                        <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </summary>

                  <div class="accBody">
                    <p class="notesText">
                      Si ICC rebasa el punto de corte (H &gt; 0.95 / M &gt; 0.85), considerar riesgo cardiometabólico y correlacionar con:
                      glucosa/insulina (HOMA-IR), HbA1c, perfil lipídico, PCR-us y clínica (PA, circunferencias, composición corporal).
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="pautasSection" id="pautasSection">
            <div class="pautasCard">
              <div class="pautasHeader">PAUTAS ADICIONALES</div>
              <div class="pautasBody">
                <p class="pautasText">
                  Evaluar solo el perfil lipídico nos indica en esos días cuáles son las cifras de cada biomarcador, pero al solicitar el
                  índice aterogénico, prueba de PCR, HbA1c (hemoglobina glicosilada), más el porcentaje de grasa, la distribución de grasa,
                  las tallas y fotografías del paciente, podremos tener información mucho más completa y útil. Por tanto:
                </p>

                <ul class="pautasList">
                  <li>Podemos tener ventaja en cuanto a tiempo para comenzar el abordaje nutricional.</li>
                  <li>Meta razonable de pérdida de grasa a medio–largo plazo: <strong>5–10%</strong>.</li>
                  <li>Se recomienda fuertemente el <strong>entrenamiento de fuerza (pesas)</strong>.</li>
                  <li>Aporte de proteína de <strong>2 g/kg</strong> de peso total hasta <strong>3 g/kg</strong> de peso total, para prevenir lo más posible la pérdida de masa magra.</li>
                  <li>El aporte de proteína más el aporte de fibra puede aumentar la saciedad, disminuyendo la probabilidad de consumir más calorías.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- =========================
               ABORDAJE IDEAL
               ========================= -->
          <section class="abSection" id="abSection">
            <div class="abTopGrid">
              <div class="abCard" id="abFenotipoCard">
                <div class="abHeader">
                  <span>FENOTIPO DETECTADO</span>
                  <span class="tag"><span class="tagDot"></span><span id="abFenotipoTag">—</span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText" id="abFenotipoText">
                    Selecciona criterios para mostrar el fenotipo sugerido.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="abCard" id="abIdealCard">
                <div class="abHeader">
                  <span>ABORDAJE IDEAL SUGERIDO</span>
                  <span class="tag"><span class="tagDot"></span><span id="abIdealTag">Guía</span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText" id="abIdealText">
                    Aquí aparecerá el enfoque recomendado según el fenotipo (educativo; se individualiza con clínica y labs).
                  </p>
                  <ul class="abList" id="abIdealList"></ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="abNote">
              Nota: esto es una guía clínica-nutricional educativa. Siempre confirmar diagnóstico, descartar causas secundarias (tiroides, hiperprolactinemia, CAH no clásica, Cushing, tumores secretores) y personalizar según objetivo (fertilidad, piel/vello, peso, riesgo cardiometabólico).
            </div>

            <div class="abGrid4" id="abByFenotipoGrid">
              <div class="abCard" data-ab="A" id="abCardA">
                <div class="abMiniHeader">Fenotipo A • Abordaje ideal</div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText">Prioridad: <strong>metabólico + hiperandrogenismo + ciclo</strong>. Suele requerir un plan más intensivo.</p>
                  <ul class="abList" id="abListA"></ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="abCard" data-ab="B" id="abCardB">
                <div class="abMiniHeader">Fenotipo B • Abordaje ideal</div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText">Prioridad: <strong>ciclo + hiperandrogenismo</strong>, y búsqueda activa de IR/metabólico.</p>
                  <ul class="abList" id="abListB"></ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="abCard" data-ab="C" id="abCardC">
                <div class="abMiniHeader">Fenotipo C • Abordaje ideal</div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText">Prioridad: <strong>hiperandrogenismo</strong> (piel/vello) con vigilancia metabólica.</p>
                  <ul class="abList" id="abListC"></ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="abCard" data-ab="D" id="abCardD">
                <div class="abMiniHeader">Fenotipo D • Abordaje ideal</div>
                <div class="abBody">
                  <p class="abText">Prioridad: <strong>regularidad menstrual/ovulación</strong> + estilo de vida; menor carga androgénica.</p>
                  <ul class="abList" id="abListD"></ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="abCard" id="abSubtiposCard">
              <div class="abHeader">
                <span>CÓMO DIFERENCIAR SUBTIPO: IR vs ADRENAL vs OVÁRICO</span>
                <span class="tag"><span class="tagDot"></span><span>Clínica + 4 labs</span></span>
              </div>
              <div class="abBody">
                <p class="abText">
                  Esto no reemplaza diagnóstico médico: ayuda a orientar "qué buscar primero" y qué laboratorios priorizar según presentación clínica.
                </p>

                <div class="abGrid4" style="margin-top:14px;">
                  <div class="abCard" style="box-shadow:none; border-color: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.28); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">
                    <div class="abMiniHeader">SOP insulinorresistente (IR)</div>
                    <div class="abBody">
                      <p class="abText"><strong>Clínica sugerente</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>Aumento de cintura/obesidad central, acantosis nigricans.</li>
                        <li>Hambre frecuente, somnolencia postprandial, antojos dulces.</li>
                        <li>Historia familiar de DM2/SM, dislipidemia.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p class="abText" style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>4 laboratorios clave</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>Insulina en ayunas (y/o HOMA-IR calculado).</li>
                        <li>Glucosa en ayunas.</li>
                        <li>HbA1c.</li>
                        <li>Curva de tolerancia (75g) con glucosa ± insulina (si se puede).</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="abCard" style="box-shadow:none; border-color: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.28); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">
                    <div class="abMiniHeader">SOP "adrenal" (predominio suprarrenal)</div>
                    <div class="abBody">
                      <p class="abText"><strong>Clínica sugerente</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>Inicio ligado a estrés/privación de sueño; ansiedad, fatiga.</li>
                        <li>Acné/hirsutismo con peso normal o cambios leves.</li>
                        <li>Empeora con cafeína/estrés; síntomas de disautonomía en algunas pacientes.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p class="abText" style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>4 laboratorios clave</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>DHEA-S (marcador adrenal útil).</li>
                        <li>Androstenediona.</li>
                        <li>Cortisol (idealmente según sospecha: AM o prueba dirigida por médico).</li>
                        <li>17-OH progesterona (descartar CAH no clásica si hiperandrogenismo).</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="abCard" style="box-shadow:none; border-color: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.28); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">
                    <div class="abMiniHeader">SOP "ovárico" (predominio ovárico)</div>
                    <div class="abBody">
                      <p class="abText"><strong>Clínica sugerente</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>Hiperandrogenismo claro: hirsutismo, acné, alopecia.</li>
                        <li>Oligo/amenorrea desde adolescencia; infertilidad anovulatoria.</li>
                        <li>USG con MOP (no obligatorio, pero apoya).</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p class="abText" style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>4 laboratorios clave</strong>:</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>Testosterona total y/o libre (ideal con SHBG para índice androgénico).</li>
                        <li>SHBG (suele bajar con IR, sube con estrógenos/tiroides).</li>
                        <li>LH y FSH (relación LH/FSH puede orientar en algunos casos).</li>
                        <li>AMH (orienta a carga folicular; interpretación por contexto).</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="abCard" style="box-shadow:none; border-color: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.28); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">
                    <div class="abMiniHeader">Siempre descartar "mimics"</div>
                    <div class="abBody">
                      <p class="abText"><strong>Si hay datos atípicos</strong> (virilización rápida, andrógenos muy altos, galactorrea, pérdida de peso inexplicable, estrías violáceas, etc.):</p>
                      <ul class="abList">
                        <li>TSH + T4L (tiroides)</li>
                        <li>Prolactina</li>
                        <li>17-OH progesterona</li>
                        <li>Evaluación de Cushing/tumor según sospecha clínica (médico)</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <p class="abText" style="margin-top:14px;">
                  Tip: la mayoría de pacientes son "mixtas". El objetivo de este bloque es priorizar la ruta: <strong>metabólico (IR)</strong> vs <strong>androgénico (ovárico)</strong> vs <strong>estrés/adrenal</strong>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- =========================
                 NUEVA SECCIÓN: DIAGNÓSTICOS DIFERENCIALES
                 ========================= -->
            <section class="ddSection" id="ddSection">
              <div class="ddCard">
                <div class="ddHeader">
                  Diagnósticos diferenciales que simulan SOP
                </div>

                <div class="ddBody">
                  <p class="ddIntro">
                    Antes de asumir que una paciente presenta <strong>síndrome de ovario poliquístico (SOP)</strong>,
                    es importante considerar otras entidades clínicas que pueden <strong>imitar el cuadro</strong>,
                    especialmente si el <strong>hiperandrogenismo es intenso, de inicio rápido o desproporcionado</strong>.
                  </p>

                  <div class="ddGrid">
                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Hiperplasia suprarrenal congénita no clásica</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        Puede presentarse con hirsutismo, acné, irregularidad menstrual y elevación androgénica.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>Solicitar 17-hidroxiprogesterona basal</li>
                        <li>Considerar prueba confirmatoria si hay sospecha clínica</li>
                        <li>Importante en hiperandrogenismo desde edades tempranas</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>

                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Tumores secretores de andrógenos</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        Deben descartarse cuando existe virilización marcada o progresión rápida de síntomas.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>Testosterona muy elevada</li>
                        <li>DHEA-S marcadamente alta</li>
                        <li>Inicio brusco de hirsutismo, voz grave o clitoromegalia</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>

                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Síndrome de Cushing</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        Comparte rasgos con SOP como resistencia a la insulina, aumento de grasa central y alteraciones menstruales.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>Obesidad troncal</li>
                        <li>Estrías violáceas</li>
                        <li>Debilidad muscular proximal e hipertensión</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>

                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Hiperprolactinemia</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        Puede alterar ovulación y menstruación, simulando un cuadro de anovulación crónica.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>Amenorrea u oligomenorrea</li>
                        <li>Galactorrea</li>
                        <li>Solicitar prolactina sérica en contexto adecuado</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>

                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Disfunción tiroidea</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        El hipotiroidismo puede contribuir a irregularidad menstrual, fatiga, aumento de peso y cambios metabólicos.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>Solicitar TSH y, si aplica, T4 libre</li>
                        <li>Puede coexistir con SOP y confundir el cuadro</li>
                        <li>Siempre debe valorarse en la evaluación inicial</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>

                    <article class="ddMimicCard">
                      <h3 class="ddMimicTitle">Insuficiencia ovárica primaria o disfunción hipotalámica</h3>
                      <p class="ddMimicText">
                        En amenorrea o alteraciones del ciclo, no todo es SOP; también deben valorarse causas centrales u ováricas.
                      </p>
                      <ul class="ddMimicList">
                        <li>FSH/LH según contexto</li>
                        <li>Historia de estrés, ejercicio extremo o baja disponibilidad energética</li>
                        <li>Valorar reserva ovárica y contexto clínico</li>
                      </ul>
                    </article>
                  </div>

                  <div class="ddAlertBox">
                    <h3 class="ddAlertTitle">Señales de alerta para ampliar estudio</h3>
                    <ul class="ddAlertList">
                      <li>Virilización rápida o intensa</li>
                      <li>Inicio súbito de hirsutismo severo</li>
                      <li>Testosterona total marcadamente elevada</li>
                      <li>DHEA-S muy elevada</li>
                      <li>Amenorrea completa de aparición reciente</li>
                      <li>Datos clínicos no compatibles con SOP típico</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <p class="ddFooterNote">
                    <strong>Nota clínica:</strong> en lugar de usar el término en inglés <em>mimics</em>,
                    esta sección emplea la expresión en español <strong>"diagnósticos diferenciales que simulan SOP"</strong>,
                    que comunica mejor el concepto en un entorno clínico y educativo.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <!-- /NUEVA SECCIÓN -->

          </section><!-- /abSection -->

        </div><!-- /criteriaWrap -->
      </div><!-- /heroInner -->
    </main>
  </div><!-- /wrap -->

  <!-- Botones flotantes -->
  <div class="floatBtns" aria-label="Botones de contacto flotantes">
    <a class="floatBtn ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/raulvargas_proehn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Instagram">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M7.5 2.8h9A4.7 4.7 0 0 1 21.2 7.5v9A4.7 4.7 0 0 1 16.5 21.2h-9A4.7 4.7 0 0 1 2.8 16.5v-9A4.7 4.7 0 0 1 7.5 2.8Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <path d="M12 16.1a4.1 4.1 0 1 0 0-8.2 4.1 4.1 0 0 0 0 8.2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <path d="M17.3 6.7h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    </a>

    <a class="floatBtn wa" href="https://wa.me/528132216529?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20ponerme%20en%20contacto%20con%20PRO%20Enhanced%20Nutrition." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="WhatsApp">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M12 21.2a9.1 9.1 0 0 0 7.8-13.8A9.1 9.1 0 0 0 3.9 18.6L2.8 21.2l2.8-1A9.1 9.1 0 0 0 12 21.2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <path d="M9.3 8.7c.2-.4.4-.4.6-.4h.5c.2 0 .4 0 .5.4.1.4.5 1.4.6 1.6.1.2.1.4 0 .6l-.3.5c-.1.2-.2.4 0 .7.2.3.8 1.2 1.8 2 .9.7 1.7 1 2 .9.3-.1.9-.4 1-.6.2-.2.3-.2.5-.1.2.1 1.4.7 1.6.8.2.1.3.2.3.4 0 .2-.1.8-.6 1.2-.5.4-1 .6-1.7.5-1.3-.2-2.9-1-4.3-2.4-1.4-1.4-2.3-3-2.4-4.3 0-.7.1-1.2.5-1.7Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      // Contacto: los botones de WhatsApp e Instagram son enlaces <a> directos,
      // no requieren JavaScript para funcionar.

      /* =========================
         DATA: ABORDAJES POR FENOTIPO
         ========================= */
      const approachMap = {
        A: [
          "Priorizar reducción de riesgo cardiometabólico: déficit moderado, proteína alta, fibra alta, fuerza 3–5 días/semana + NEAT.",
          "Screening metabólico completo: glucosa/insulina (HOMA-IR), HbA1c, lípidos, PA, cintura/ICC; seguimiento por objetivos.",
          "Enfoque antiinflamatorio práctico: ultraprocesados ↓, omega-3/alimentos ricos, sueño y estrés como parte del plan.",
          "Si objetivo es fertilidad: optimizar ovulación con equipo médico; ordenar timing de labs y ultrasonido según fase.",
          "Si objetivo es piel/vello: plan sostenido 12+ semanas, y descartar mimics si hiperandrogenismo es desproporcionado."
        ],
        B: [
          "Misma intensidad que A en ciclo + hiperandrogenismo; buscar IR aunque el USG no muestre MOP.",
          "Nutrición: control de carga glucémica + proteína/fibra; priorizar fuerza y progresión (mejoran sensibilidad a insulina).",
          "Monitoreo: lípidos, HbA1c, insulina/HOMA-IR; metas realistas (5–10% grasa si aplica).",
          "Piel/vello: integrar estrategia dermatológica/médica si hay impacto significativo.",
          "Educar sobre consistencia: cambios en andrógenos y piel requieren tiempo."
        ],
        C: [
          "Fenotipo ovulatorio: foco en hiperandrogenismo + prevención metabólica (no asumir "todo bien").",
          "Plan: fuerza + pasos diarios; distribución de carbohidratos alrededor de entrenamiento si aplica.",
          "Monitoreo dirigido: lípidos, glucosa/HbA1c; considerar insulina/HOMA-IR si hay signos clínicos de IR.",
          "Piel/acné/hirsutismo: evaluar severidad, causas asociadas (adrenal vs ovárico) y tratar por rutas.",
          "Si IMC normal: evitar dietas extremas; priorizar recomposición y salud hormonal."
        ],
        D: [
          "Menor carga androgénica: priorizar regularidad menstrual/ovulación y salud metabólica general.",
          "Plan base: fuerza + cardio zona 2 (si gusta) + sueño; déficit suave si hay exceso de grasa.",
          "Monitoreo: TSH/T4L y prolactina si amenorrea persistente; glucosa/HbA1c según riesgo.",
          "Si búsqueda de embarazo: coordinar con médico para evaluar ovulación y causas alternas de anovulación.",
          "Evitar sobre-medicalización: responder a la clínica y a datos objetivos."
        ]
      };

      const phenotypeNames = {
        A: "Fenotipo A",
        B: "Fenotipo B",
        C: "Fenotipo C",
        D: "Fenotipo D"
      };

      function renderApproachLists(){
        (["A","B","C","D"]).forEach(k => {
          const ul = document.getElementById(`abList${k}`);
          if (!ul) return;
          ul.innerHTML = approachMap[k].map(x => `<li>${x}</li>`).join("");
        });
      }
      renderApproachLists();

      function setActiveApproachCard(letter){
        ["A","B","C","D"].forEach(k => {
          const card = document.getElementById(`abCard${k}`);
          if (card) card.classList.toggle("isActive", k === letter);
        });
      }

      function fillTopApproach(letter, fenotipoLabelFull){
        const tag = document.getElementById("abFenotipoTag");
        const txt = document.getElementById("abFenotipoText");
        const idealTxt = document.getElementById("abIdealText");
        const idealUl = document.getElementById("abIdealList");

        if (!letter){
          tag.textContent = "—";
          txt.textContent = "Selecciona criterios para mostrar el fenotipo sugerido.";
          idealTxt.textContent = "Aquí aparecerá el enfoque recomendado según el fenotipo (educativo; se individualiza con clínica y labs).";
          idealUl.innerHTML = "";
          setActiveApproachCard(null);
          return;
        }

        tag.textContent = `${phenotypeNames[letter]} (${letter})`;
        txt.textContent = fenotipoLabelFull;

        idealTxt.textContent = `Resumen del abordaje ideal para ${phenotypeNames[letter]}:`;
        idealUl.innerHTML = approachMap[letter].map(x => `<li>${x}</li>`).join("");

        setActiveApproachCard(letter);
      }

      /* =========================
         SOP: botones SI/NO + resultado + reset
         ========================= */
      const btns = document.querySelectorAll(".toggleBtn");
      const resMain = document.getElementById("resMain");
      const resMeta = document.getElementById("resMeta");
      const resFenotipo = document.getElementById("resFenotipo");
      const box = document.getElementById("fenotipoResultado");
      const btnReset = document.getElementById("btnReset");
      const btnExportWord = document.getElementById("btnExportWord");

      const state = { mens: false, mop: false, ha: false };

      function paintBtn(btn, isOn){
        btn.dataset.val = isOn ? "si" : "no";
        btn.textContent = isOn ? "SI" : "NO";
      }

      function calcFenotipo(){
        const m = state.mens;
        const o = state.mop;
        const h = state.ha;

        if (m && o && h) return "Fenotipo A (3 criterios: Mens + HA + MOP)";
        if (m && h && !o) return "Fenotipo B (Mens + HA)";
        if (h && o && !m) return "Fenotipo C (HA + MOP)";
        if (m && o && !h) return "Fenotipo D (Mens + MOP)";
        return "—";
      }

      function getFenotipoLetterFromText(fTxt){
        const match = String(fTxt || "").match(/Fenotipo ([A-D])/);
        return match ? match[1] : null;
      }

      function setResultClass(cls){
        box.classList.remove("resA","resB","resC","resD","resNeutral");
        box.classList.add(cls);
      }

      function activateCard(letter){
        document.querySelectorAll(".fenotipoCard").forEach(c => c.classList.remove("cardActiva"));
        if (!letter) return;
        const card = document.querySelector(`.fenotipoCard[data-feno="${letter}"]`);
        if (card){
          card.classList.add("cardActiva");
          setTimeout(() => card.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth", block: "center" }), 200);
        }
      }

      function setResultPulse(on){
        box.classList.toggle("isResult", !!on);
      }

      function updateUI(){
        const positives = Object.values(state).filter(Boolean).length;
        resMeta.textContent = `Criterios positivos: ${positives}/3`;

        if (positives < 2){
          resMain.textContent = "Selecciona al menos 2 criterios para SOP (Rotterdam 2003).";
          resFenotipo.textContent = "—";
          setResultClass("resNeutral");
          setResultPulse(false);
          activateCard(null);
          fillTopApproach(null, "");
          return;
        }

        const f = calcFenotipo();
        resMain.textContent = "Fenotipo sugerido según criterios positivos:";
        resFenotipo.textContent = f;

        if (f.includes("Fenotipo A")) setResultClass("resA");
        else if (f.includes("Fenotipo B")) setResultClass("resB");
        else if (f.includes("Fenotipo C")) setResultClass("resC");
        else if (f.includes("Fenotipo D")) setResultClass("resD");
        else setResultClass("resNeutral");

        const letter = getFenotipoLetterFromText(f);
        activateCard(letter);
        setResultPulse(!!letter);
        fillTopApproach(letter, f);
      }

      btns.forEach(btn => {
        const key = btn.dataset.key;
        state[key] = (btn.dataset.val === "si");
        paintBtn(btn, state[key]);

        btn.addEventListener("click", () => {
          state[key] = !state[key];
          paintBtn(btn, state[key]);
          updateUI();
        });
      });

      btnReset.addEventListener("click", () => {
        Object.keys(state).forEach(k => state[k] = false);
        btns.forEach(btn => paintBtn(btn, false));
        updateUI();
        setTimeout(() => box.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth", block: "center" }), 150);
      });

      updateUI();

      /* =========================
         Recuadro amarillo (HA bio/clin)
         ========================= */
      const haBioBtn = document.getElementById("haBioBtn");
      const haClinBtn = document.getElementById("haClinBtn");

      function toggleYellow(btn){
        const isOn = btn.dataset.val === "si";
        btn.dataset.val = isOn ? "no" : "si";
        btn.textContent = (btn.dataset.val === "si") ? "SI" : "NO";
      }

      haBioBtn.addEventListener("click", () => toggleYellow(haBioBtn));
      haClinBtn.addEventListener("click", () => toggleYellow(haClinBtn));

      /* =========================
         US NAVY: % grasa + tabla + flecha
         ========================= */
      const bfSex = document.getElementById("bfSex");
      const bfHeight = document.getElementById("bfHeight");
      const bfWeight = document.getElementById("bfWeight");
      const bfNeck = document.getElementById("bfNeck");
      const bfWaist = document.getElementById("bfWaist");
      const bfHipWrap = document.getElementById("bfHipWrap");
      const bfHip = document.getElementById("bfHip");

      const bfCalc = document.getElementById("bfCalc");
      const bfClear = document.getElementById("bfClear");

      const bfPctEl = document.getElementById("bfPct");
      const bfDetailEl = document.getElementById("bfDetail");

      const bfArrow = document.getElementById("bfArrow");
      const bfArrowLabel = document.getElementById("bfArrowLabel");
      const bfTableWrap = document.getElementById("bfTableWrap");

      function cmToIn(cm){ return cm / 2.54; }

      function parsePosNum(el){
        const v = Number(el.value);
        return Number.isFinite(v) && v > 0 ? v : null;
      }

      function showHipBySex(){
        const isFemale = bfSex.value === "female";
        bfHipWrap.style.display = "flex";
        const label = bfHipWrap.querySelector(".bfLabel");
        label.textContent = isFemale
          ? "Cadera (cm) (para mujer en %grasa • necesaria para ICC)"
          : "Cadera (cm) (opcional para %grasa • necesaria para ICC)";
      }

      function clearArrowAndHighlight(){
        bfArrow.style.opacity = 0;
        bfArrowLabel.style.opacity = 0;
        document.querySelectorAll("#bfTable tbody tr").forEach(tr => tr.classList.remove("bfRowActive"));
        document.querySelectorAll("#bfTable tbody td").forEach(td => td.classList.remove("bfCellActive"));
      }

      function highlightRowAndCell(rowId, sex){
        const row = document.getElementById(rowId);
        if (!row) return;
        row.classList.add("bfRowActive");
        const tds = row.querySelectorAll("td");
        const idx = (sex === "male") ? 1 : 2;
        if (tds[idx]) tds[idx].classList.add("bfCellActive");
      }

      function positionArrowToRow(rowId, labelText){
        const row = document.getElementById(rowId);
        if (!row) return;
        const wrapRect = bfTableWrap.getBoundingClientRect();
        const rowRect = row.getBoundingClientRect();
        const top = (rowRect.top - wrapRect.top) + (rowRect.height / 2) - 9;
        bfArrow.style.top = `${top}px`;
        bfArrow.style.opacity = 1;
        bfArrowLabel.textContent = labelText;
        bfArrowLabel.style.top = `${top - 10}px`;
        bfArrowLabel.style.opacity = 1;
      }

      function getGeneralClassRow(sex, pct){
        if (sex === "male"){
          if (pct < 8) return { row:"row-delgado", name:"Delgado" };
          if (pct < 15) return { row:"row-optimo", name:"Óptimo" };
          if (pct < 20) return { row:"row-sobrepeso", name:"Sobrepeso" };
          if (pct < 25) return { row:"row-preobeso", name:"Pre-obeso" };
          return { row:"row-obeso", name:"Obeso" };
        } else {
          if (pct < 15) return { row:"row-delgado", name:"Delgado" };
          if (pct < 20) return { row:"row-optimo", name:"Óptimo" };
          if (pct < 25) return { row:"row-sobrepeso", name:"Sobrepeso" };
          if (pct < 32) return { row:"row-preobeso", name:"Pre-obeso" };
          return { row:"row-obeso", name:"Obeso" };
        }
      }

      function getAthleteRowIfMatches(sex, pct){
        const male = [
          { row:"row-atleta-corre", name:"Corredores", min:4, max:9 },
          { row:"row-atleta-lucha", name:"Luchadores", min:4, max:10 },
          { row:"row-atleta-gim", name:"Gimnastas", min:4, max:10 },
          { row:"row-atleta-cult", name:"Culturistas (élite)", min:5, max:8 },
          { row:"row-atleta-nada", name:"Nadadores", min:5, max:11 },
          { row:"row-atleta-basket", name:"Basket", min:7, max:11 },
          { row:"row-atleta-remo", name:"Remo", min:11, max:15 },
          { row:"row-atleta-tenis", name:"Tenistas", min:14, max:17 },
        ];

        const female = [
          { row:"row-atleta-corre", name:"Corredores", min:6, max:15 },
          { row:"row-atleta-gim", name:"Gimnastas", min:10, max:17 },
          { row:"row-atleta-cult", name:"Culturistas (élite)", min:10, max:15 },
          { row:"row-atleta-nada", name:"Nadadores", min:14, max:24 },
          { row:"row-atleta-basket", name:"Basket", min:18, max:27 },
          { row:"row-atleta-remo", name:"Remo", min:18, max:24 },
          { row:"row-atleta-tenis", name:"Tenistas", min:19, max:22 },
        ];

        const list = sex === "male" ? male : female;
        return list.find(x => pct >= x.min && pct <= x.max) || null;
      }

      function calcUSNavyBodyFatPct(sex, heightCm, neckCm, waistCm, hipCmOrNull){
        const H = cmToIn(heightCm);
        const N = cmToIn(neckCm);
        const W = cmToIn(waistCm);

        if (sex === "male"){
          const x = W - N;
          if (!(x > 0) || !(H > 0)) return null;
          return 86.010 * Math.log10(x) - 70.041 * Math.log10(H) + 36.76;
        } else {
          const Hip = cmToIn(hipCmOrNull);
          const x = W + Hip - N;
          if (!(x > 0) || !(H > 0)) return null;
          return 163.205 * Math.log10(x) - 97.684 * Math.log10(H) - 78.387;
        }
      }

      function setBFResult(pct, weightKg){
        const pct1 = Math.round(pct * 10) / 10;
        bfPctEl.textContent = `${pct1}% grasa corporal (aprox.)`;

        if (weightKg && weightKg > 0){
          const fatKg = (weightKg * (pct / 100));
          const leanKg = (weightKg - fatKg);
          bfDetailEl.textContent = `Estimación: grasa ${Math.round(fatKg * 10) / 10} kg • masa magra ${Math.round(leanKg * 10) / 10} kg.`;
        } else {
          bfDetailEl.textContent = `Porcentaje calculado. (Agrega peso si quieres kg de grasa / masa magra).`;
        }
      }

      function setBFError(msg){
        bfPctEl.textContent = "—";
        bfDetailEl.textContent = msg;
        clearArrowAndHighlight();
      }

      function computeICC(){
        const waist = parsePosNum(bfWaist);
        const hip = parsePosNum(bfHip);
        const sex = bfSex.value;

        const iccValueEl = document.getElementById("iccValue");

        if (!waist || !hip){
          iccValueEl.textContent = "#DIV/0!";
          iccValueEl.classList.remove("isHigh");
          return;
        }

        const icc = waist / hip;
        iccValueEl.textContent = (Math.round(icc * 100) / 100).toFixed(2);

        const isHigh = (sex === "female") ? (icc > 0.85) : (icc > 0.95);
        iccValueEl.classList.toggle("isHigh", isHigh);
      }

      function clearBF(){
        bfHeight.value = "";
        bfWeight.value = "";
        bfNeck.value = "";
        bfWaist.value = "";
        bfHip.value = "";
        bfSex.value = "female";

        showHipBySex();

        bfPctEl.textContent = "—";
        bfDetailEl.textContent = `Completa los campos y presiona Calcular.`;
        clearArrowAndHighlight();
        computeICC();
      }

      showHipBySex();
      bfSex.addEventListener("change", () => { showHipBySex(); computeICC(); });

      bfClear.addEventListener("click", clearBF);

      bfCalc.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const sex = bfSex.value;
        const heightCm = parsePosNum(bfHeight);
        const weightKg = parsePosNum(bfWeight);
        const neckCm = parsePosNum(bfNeck);
        const waistCm = parsePosNum(bfWaist);
        const hipCm = parsePosNum(bfHip);

        if (!heightCm || !neckCm || !waistCm){
          setBFError("Faltan datos: altura, cuello y cintura/abdomen son obligatorios.");
          return;
        }
        if (sex === "female" && !hipCm){
          setBFError("Faltan datos: para mujer, cadera es obligatoria.");
          return;
        }

        const pct = calcUSNavyBodyFatPct(sex, heightCm, neckCm, waistCm, hipCm);
        if (pct === null || !Number.isFinite(pct)){
          setBFError("No se pudo calcular. Revisa que cintura sea mayor que cuello (y en mujer, que cintura + cadera sea mayor que cuello).");
          return;
        }

        const pctClamped = Math.max(0, Math.min(75, pct));
        setBFResult(pctClamped, weightKg || null);

        const athlete = getAthleteRowIfMatches(sex, pctClamped);
        const gen = getGeneralClassRow(sex, pctClamped);

        clearArrowAndHighlight();
        highlightRowAndCell(gen.row, sex);
        if (athlete) highlightRowAndCell(athlete.row, sex);

        const pct1 = Math.round(pctClamped * 10) / 10;
        const label = athlete ? `${pct1}% • ${gen.name} • Atleta: ${athlete.name}` : `${pct1}% • ${gen.name}`;
        positionArrowToRow(athlete ? athlete.row : gen.row, label);

        computeICC();
      });

      clearArrowAndHighlight();

      /* =========================
         Evaluador MetS
         ========================= */
      const msBtns = document.querySelectorAll(".msYN");
      const msInterpret = document.getElementById("msInterpret");
      const msBottomText = document.getElementById("msBottomText");

      const msState = { waist:false, tg:false, hdl:false, bp:false, glu:false };

      function paintMSBtn(btn, on){
        btn.dataset.val = on ? "si" : "no";
        btn.textContent = on ? "SI" : "NO";
      }

      function updateMS(){
        const yes = Object.values(msState).filter(Boolean).length;
        msInterpret.textContent = `Interpretación de criterios • Positivos: ${yes}/5`;
        msBottomText.textContent = (yes >= 3)
          ? "Posible síndrome metabólico, indagar más en la información del paciente."
          : "No cumple los criterios para síndrome metabólico, evaluar más.";
      }

      msBtns.forEach(btn => {
        const key = btn.dataset.key;
        msState[key] = (btn.dataset.val === "si");
        paintMSBtn(btn, msState[key]);

        btn.addEventListener("click", () => {
          msState[key] = !msState[key];
          paintMSBtn(btn, msState[key]);
          updateMS();
        });
      });

      updateMS();

      /* =========================
         ICC live
         ========================= */
      bfWaist.addEventListener("input", computeICC);
      bfHip.addEventListener("input", computeICC);
      computeICC();

      /* =========================
         Acordeón: solo uno open a la vez
         ========================= */
      const accs = document.querySelectorAll("details.acc");
      accs.forEach(d => {
        d.addEventListener("toggle", () => {
          if (!d.open) return;
          accs.forEach(other => {
            if (other !== d) other.open = false;
          });
        });
      });

      /* =========================
         EXPORTAR RESULTADOS A WORD
         ========================= */
      function escapeHtml(str){
        return String(str ?? "")
          .replace(/&/g, "&amp;")
          .replace(/</g, "&lt;")
          .replace(/>/g, "&gt;")
          .replace(/"/g, "&quot;")
          .replace(/'/g, "&#039;");
      }

      function yn(val){ return val ? "SI" : "NO"; }

      function listToHtml(items){
        return `<ul>${items.map(x => `<li>${escapeHtml(x)}</li>`).join("")}</ul>`;
      }

      function exportToWord(){
        const stamp = new Date().toLocaleString("es-MX", { timeZone: "America/Mexico_City" });

        const positives = Object.values(state).filter(Boolean).length;
        const fenotipoTxt = document.getElementById("resFenotipo").textContent.trim();
        const fenotipoMain = document.getElementById("resMain").textContent.trim();
        const fLetter = getFenotipoLetterFromText(fenotipoTxt);

        const haBio = (haBioBtn.dataset.val === "si");
        const haClin = (haClinBtn.dataset.val === "si");

        const sexLabel = (bfSex.value === "female") ? "Mujer" : "Hombre";
        const bfPctTxt = document.getElementById("bfPct").textContent.trim();
        const bfDetailTxt = document.getElementById("bfDetail").textContent.trim();
        const bfClass = (bfArrowLabel && bfArrowLabel.textContent) ? bfArrowLabel.textContent.trim() : "—";

        const iccEl = document.getElementById("iccValue");
        const iccVal = iccEl ? iccEl.textContent.trim() : "—";
        const iccHigh = iccEl ? iccEl.classList.contains("isHigh") : false;

        const msYes = Object.values(msState).filter(Boolean).length;
        const msInterpretTxt = msInterpret.textContent.trim();
        const msBottomTxt = msBottomText.textContent.trim();

        const notasEl = document.querySelector("#notesSection details.acc .accBody");
        const notasPlain = notasEl ? notasEl.innerText.trim() : "";

        const pautasEl = document.querySelector("#pautasSection .pautasBody");
        const pautasPlain = pautasEl ? pautasEl.innerText.trim() : "";

        const chosenApproach = fLetter ? approachMap[fLetter] : [];
        const chosenTitle = fLetter ? `${phenotypeNames[fLetter]} (${fLetter})` : "—";

        const allApproachesHtml = ["A","B","C","D"].map(k => {
          const title = `${phenotypeNames[k]} (${k})`;
          const activeBadge = (k === fLetter) ? `<span style="margin-left:10px; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:999px; border:1px solid #fb923c; background:#fff7ed; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;">DETECTADO</span>` : "";
          return `
            <div class="box">
              <h2 style="margin:0 0 6px;">Abordaje ideal — ${escapeHtml(title)} ${activeBadge}</h2>
              ${listToHtml(approachMap[k])}
            </div>
          `;
        }).join("");

        const docHtml = `
<!doctype html>
<html lang="es-MX">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>PRO Enhanced Nutrition — Resultados</title>
  <style>
    body{ font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color:#111827; }
    h1{ font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
    h2{ font-size: 14px; margin: 18px 0 8px; }
    p, li{ font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; margin: 6px 0; }
    .muted{ color:#4b5563; }
    .box{ border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:12px; margin: 10px 0; }
    table{ border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; }
    td, th{ border:1px solid #e5e7eb; padding:8px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: top; }
    th{ background:#f3f4f6; text-align:left; }
    .tag{ display:inline-block; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:999px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size:11px; }
    .high{ border-color:#ef4444; color:#991b1b; }
    .hr{ height:1px; background:#e5e7eb; border:0; margin: 12px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>PRO Enhanced Nutrition — Exportación de resultados</h1>
  <p class="muted">Generado: ${escapeHtml(stamp)} (hora México)</p>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>1) Fenotipo SOP (Rotterdam 2003)</h2>
    <p><strong>${escapeHtml(fenotipoMain)}</strong></p>
    <p><strong>Resultado:</strong> ${escapeHtml(fenotipoTxt)}</p>
    <p><strong>Criterios positivos:</strong> ${escapeHtml(String(positives))}/3</p>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Criterio</th><th>Estado</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Alteraciones menstruales y/o amenorrea</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(state.mens))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Morfología de ovario poliquístico (MOP)</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(state.mop))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Hiperandrogenismo (clínico o bioquímico)</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(state.ha))}</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p><strong>HA adicional:</strong> Bioquímico = ${escapeHtml(yn(haBio))} • Clínico = ${escapeHtml(yn(haClin))}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>2) Abordaje ideal según fenotipo detectado</h2>
    <p><strong>Fenotipo:</strong> ${escapeHtml(chosenTitle)}</p>
    ${
      fLetter
        ? `<p class="muted">Guía educativa; individualizar con clínica, objetivos (fertilidad/dermatológico/metabólico) y laboratorios.</p>${listToHtml(chosenApproach)}`
        : `<p>No hay fenotipo detectado (se requieren ≥2 criterios). Abajo se incluye el anexo con abordajes por fenotipo.</p>`
    }
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>3) Composición corporal (US Navy, aproximación)</h2>
    <p><strong>Sexo:</strong> ${escapeHtml(sexLabel)}</p>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Dato</th><th>Valor</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Altura (cm)</td><td>${escapeHtml(bfHeight.value || "—")}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Peso (kg)</td><td>${escapeHtml(bfWeight.value || "—")}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Cuello (cm)</td><td>${escapeHtml(bfNeck.value || "—")}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Cintura/Abdomen (cm)</td><td>${escapeHtml(bfWaist.value || "—")}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Cadera (cm)</td><td>${escapeHtml(bfHip.value || "—")}</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p><strong>% grasa:</strong> ${escapeHtml(bfPctTxt)}</p>
    <p><strong>Detalle:</strong> ${escapeHtml(bfDetailTxt)}</p>
    <p><strong>Clasificación señalada:</strong> ${escapeHtml(bfClass)}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>4) Índice cintura-cadera (ICC)</h2>
    <p><strong>ICC:</strong> <span class="tag ${iccHigh ? "high" : ""}">${escapeHtml(iccVal)}${iccHigh ? " (alto)" : ""}</span></p>
    <p class="muted">Puntos de corte: Mujeres &gt; 0.85 • Hombres &gt; 0.95.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>5) Evaluador de salud metabólica (Síndrome Metabólico)</h2>
    <p><strong>Positivos:</strong> ${escapeHtml(String(msYes))}/5</p>
    <p><strong>${escapeHtml(msInterpretTxt)}</strong></p>
    <p>${escapeHtml(msBottomTxt)}</p>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Criterio</th><th>Estado</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Cintura elevada</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(msState.waist))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Triglicéridos ≥150 mg/dL</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(msState.tg))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>HDL bajo</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(msState.hdl))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Presión arterial ≥130/85 mmHg</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(msState.bp))}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Glucosa en ayunas ≥100 mg/dL</td><td>${escapeHtml(yn(msState.glu))}</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>6) Notas adjuntas</h2>
    <p style="white-space:pre-line;">${escapeHtml(notasPlain)}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>7) Pautas adicionales</h2>
    <p style="white-space:pre-line;">${escapeHtml(pautasPlain)}</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="hr"/>

  <h2>ANEXO • Abordajes ideales por fenotipo (separados)</h2>
  ${allApproachesHtml}

  <p class="muted">
    Documento generado automáticamente con fines educativos e informativos. Interpretar con criterio profesional.
  </p>
</body>
</html>`;

        const blob = new Blob([docHtml], { type: "application/msword;charset=utf-8" });
        const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);

        const a = document.createElement("a");
        a.href = url;
        a.download = "PROEHN_resultados.doc";
        document.body.appendChild(a);
        a.click();
        a.remove();

        setTimeout(() => URL.revokeObjectURL(url), 1000);
      }

      if (btnExportWord){
        btnExportWord.addEventListener("click", exportToWord);
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
